# Assembly Practice Exercises

## ğŸ§  1. Simple Addition
Write ARM assembly code to add two numbers (5 and 10) and store the result in R2.

```assembly
MOV R0, #5
MOV R1, #10
ADD R2, R0, R1  // R2 = 5 + 10
```
âœ… **Expected Output:** R2 = 15

